org.springframework.test.web.client

Class ExpectedCount

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.test.web.client.ExpectedCount

  • public final class ExpectedCount
extends Object
    A simple type representing a range for an expected count.

    Examples: 

     import static org.springframework.test.web.client.ExpectedCount.*

 once()
 twice()
 manyTimes()
 times(5)
 min(2)
 max(4)
 between(2, 4)
 never()

    4.3
    Author:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
